nt-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;新的法律可能会更进一步。&lt;/strong&gt;自 20 世纪 80 年代以来，各州和城市稳步制定了一系列针对一次性塑料&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/muTwrmmz7vPU19nJJebRCPB2zejZam-DOQD66qDu6CNY26WO9nmpuRSF-MmKQl4yWHWDZD2NzZMXV60OrvY19OGyp6wsw0xEJec_7bqO_2wXm9vFIN5EMzrAvf4kjcs6JHrVcllnqSM_cVsTjF91jKXgxi0Ev2oDf_J9cpo8YNp5B8dqN-bcA87tF2gaTdCdcdHYjQfqrVML04xn8gHj5-hZRX7cUhZJFlkNtO_lKM3tTTzrWjcH5Aca_SK43yhk_-zatTFkgRpUqgg3oKRnhvdQ0djkQ43U6McWG2do8q2q-V7HiWYajiQIe0Dvz9pMNwsOdOZ803yvyxpBwkyeWTXi6nNEn_z-KsqJxtK1SEwU0Fg1eG-i6l272e5BSIUzm6DE9Ett5tUgZ4VqaanBf2IRdH9kBAIND6QOBi8rkSsy0-oTob9tLFCID4vbCZ88RWelTadnJVfxX3NgzJ1AqW8m02rD8alc6zb5isTOTP_AxpWIWsuA9w3sMXNTcNbx7AXZ1sr80rRnMuob8Xl4kEOGLC_ayHUk3mXhhejE8TeLlgEx7iVeosw/TcZaliQx8Ja7mqKYRrdXQytGtUVzeQy5/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="加州在一片抱怨声中启动第一阶段的塑料打击行动"&gt;的禁令&lt;/a&gt;，而民主党最近提出了一项法案，认为聚苯乙烯用于食品包装不安全。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;业内人士表示，美国的做法是错误的&lt;/strong&gt;。支持者指出，欧盟监管机构表示，如果制造和使用得当，聚苯乙烯不会对健康构成威胁，而&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/mA5PoZ6pAcJODkG-V2SuYlEzAqZm_HiYm6b5DwOamp9n7E-ILoY26uFI7t_5CDsTyBan71mOcIzJvk_EAzrZ3e5pAhMwIXNW6zHZ0Yo3WwR2Cx3X_Cud7jf_0MuqB4SN968Q8hxggkOpjfnzxn_8w7em02f8GIgvgzx3ln3O4qiJAnYwbHdirmjKqxtGcxfUGmeOtWIT7cAZPGfKm32KhkeGgr63Ys-G2QXX1Jmyf8HMxO0uOcl2_Dr1FNBCMrYAItL7f2reCQGPVwfgMlGB0aeKijevLGwCKb2u2zsFV_bVN2NFzrlgvlP5v51vmu0Px1uADjVSMKJ7N_mSHdCAdQQ1D-YFX0MKucdBOxoYe8Ptu9xwCfUSMjaHuc3fZ1Fjlq9JloqhyQ5Zg8-CzAsQOgSWrDQZmb71nl4zlBM0lF8_uBg2IAv0m5CWMQy-Q3m4so68BVPzh9weJzRcwzERoi5KQitYReBswnSYcRC_rWWBAxqyxDXdyY8r4zOsQCnjljDn0lCzs2TJ2k_nG2AW0Axf9HB2ZRqtC5GLAN8XFlJ0tIjAU6OZ/TfTv2j0vp3fzXANyw82R_ts-KukLz5Di/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="日本对塑料的热爱正受到供应限制的考验"&gt;日本等国家&lt;/a&gt;则继续采用这种材料。&lt;